name: Flying the Air Canada Express Embraer 175!
description:
The Montreal to Toronto route is one of the busiest air routes in the country, with Air Canada alone flying over a dozen flights a day.

So, needing to get to Toronto for my connecting flight to Calgary, I picked the 0530 flight on an Air Canada Express E175, in Business! See what I thought of it in this video.
